usive data on this system\nare well described by our model, too. This case also constitutes the heaviest\nnuclear system, where exclusive measurements of double-pionic fusion can be\ncarried out with present-day instruments. Surprisingly, the $pp \\to\npp\\pi^0\\pi^0$ reaction in the $\\Delta\\Delta$ region is observed to also show a\nABC-like low-$\\pi\\pi$ mass enhancement, a phenomenon, which deserves special\nattention.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2006 16:33:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
